'''Firefighter Cutler''' is a firefighter at station 19.

==History==
==="Haunted" House===
Cutler responded with the team to a call at the Hackett House, known to local kids to be the site of a family murder. When Travis and Theo didn't respond to calls over the radio, he said that he hadn't seen them outside the house when he searched the perimeter. ''("[[Searching for the Ghost]]")''

===Andy's Self Defense Class===
Kline volunteered for Andy's self defense class to let the participants practice choke holds. ''("[[Twist and Shout]]")''

===Apartment Fire===
As they got called out to an apartment fire, Beckett told Maya he wanted her on ladder with him, so Maya sent Cutler to the engine. ''("[[Everybody's Got Something to Hide Except Me and My Monkey]]")''

==Career==
He is a firefighter at [[SFD Station 19|Station 19]] of the [[Seattle Fire Department]].

==Notes and Trivia==
*While he has appeared in several episodes as a background character, [[Searching for the Ghost]] is the first episode in which he speaks.
